name: Baby Clopsi #2
description:
This is a Baby Clopsi. Its owner has the chance to receive a mature Clopsi from us randomly and free of charge. 

The more the number of the baby Clopsies you own, the more is your chance to win the mature Clopsi. 

The value of a mature Clopsi is  several ten folds more than a baby Clopsi and the number of mature Closies is much less as well. 

Meanwhile, some of the mother lacking baby Clopsies will be expired gradually.
